_:N63608a1217c84743905659c1bafb7bbe <http://schema.org/description> "CICA pays compensation to people physically or mentally injured because of a violent crime in England, Scotland or Wales, or in an act of terror abroad. CICA is an executive agency, sponsored by the Ministry of Justice ." .
